{"tid":383369,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[世界語] 連登有冇人識Esperanto?","createTime":"2017-09-01T12:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T03:31:59.000Z","uid":84495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d1cdb08126d2dee785c29fb9e773e876785604b3","tid":383369,"uid":84495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"Saluton! <br />\nMi estas lihkg-ano kaj komencanto de Esperanto.<br />\nMi jam finis la kurson sur Duolingo, nun lernantas plu pri Esperanto sur aliaj retejoj.<br />\nĈu estas esperantistoj en lihkg?<br />\nNi babilu kaj dividu viajn spertojn kune!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有文法寫錯嘅話求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 如果有唔識esperanto嘅人入咗嚟，其實可以估吓上面講緊乜，因為淨係用英文估都應該睇得明幾多吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fc7bc1edfa74667652c486fa56abaf354923e9","tid":383369,"uid":84495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"Neniu?"},{"pid":"bc2c9c959bd28fe750f5cf42922fb56b3c12e6ae","tid":383369,"uid":35317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:59:03.000Z","msg":"有鬼用<br />\n又冇人用又冇文化歷史價值"},{"pid":"0c81f76efec1fb79a3af25000e23a8b662dc0eb6","tid":383369,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有鬼用<br />\n又冇人用又冇文化歷史價值</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1eae7b96c052df0e3473f7cf404c2d0011d5f6","tid":383369,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34fe8ab8b248e8ab9b3f7b100dc21111b55ffde3","tid":383369,"uid":120537,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:09:33.000Z","msg":"毒撚真係毒撚，學外語都要揀樣語言中嘅毒撚嚟學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1fa5ab574621756cf1a65401bbf333f89d6c27","tid":383369,"uid":103893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:14:06.000Z","msg":"本人對語言有興趣，但對conlang一啲興趣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01bdf39eeb6c9832b669bca7d4c71f69fa929ba","tid":383369,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有鬼用<br />\n又冇人用又冇文化歷史價值</blockquote><br />\n有啲人唔鐘意英文霸權嘛<br />\n啱啊<br />\n用國際語囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c84a6cf96259400e3384ff8d7be6e187a39543","tid":383369,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前學過 但係冇乜用停左"},{"pid":"d3110630f0ee748de4b0e31b19f4066fc7dd5318","tid":383369,"uid":84495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚真係毒撚，學外語都要揀樣語言中嘅毒撚嚟學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴線，做乜無啦啦話我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣學conlang咪學囉，啲人學high valyrian學dothraki咪又係咁學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nEsperanto幾得意架，主要用Romance同German嘅字做基礎，又有好易上手嘅grammar規則，學學吓就發現到裡面好玩嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2422d3aaf2c62e39bff60ee9f73797b0cb09d6db","tid":383369,"uid":84495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T02:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有鬼用<br />\n又冇人用又冇文化歷史價值</blockquote><br />\n係啊，conlang都係好難成功<br />\n不過呢百幾年嚟，都仲有好多有心人每年開國際性嘅conference，都有唔同嘅作品出現，都算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見近年啲人話因為有duolingo，學esperanto嘅人數上升咗好多，咪諗住睇吓連登有冇人學過囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102d03bfaf85d7a747736a2825dd6606d081fa6b","tid":383369,"uid":35317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T02:56:02.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣on9野就係<br />\n話明世界語，點知九成詞彙、語法都係來自歐洲語言，完全無視東亞/閃米特語言<br />\n整嗰條友真係自視過高"},{"pid":"6a5ab9b9f6c4cf850247b91356960708e424394d","tid":383369,"uid":84495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有一樣on9野就係<br />\n話明世界語，點知九成詞彙、語法都係來自歐洲語言，完全無視東亞/閃米特語言<br />\n整嗰條友真係自視過高</blockquote><br />\n我都覺，不過當年係19世紀末，佢用歐洲語言嚟整都未嘗唔合理嘅<br />\n同埋世界語呢個名純粹係中文譯名? 其實係邊個譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2501873b427be8a216d196edc66091e02481dd12","tid":383369,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T02:59:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有鬼用<br />\n又冇人用又冇文化歷史價值</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5151b3c15da13ab4fae7bd0a2088ffa0068a4b61","tid":383369,"uid":16150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T03:01:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有一樣on9野就係<br />\n話明世界語，點知九成詞彙、語法都係來自歐洲語言，完全無視東亞/閃米特語言<br />\n整嗰條友真係自視過高</blockquote><br />\n我都覺，不過當年係19世紀末，佢用歐洲語言嚟整都未嘗唔合理嘅<br />\n同埋世界語呢個名純粹係中文譯名? 其實係邊個譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為整出黎果條友係想用呢個語言代替英文做世界語言嘛<br />\n文法夠簡單易學"},{"pid":"a211167b7aceeafe53bbf2991a78277046d9d6d1","tid":383369,"uid":41382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:21:57.000Z","msg":"點解叫世界語但都係用英文?"},{"pid":"7ab4c675135f85e6ae99a0337af3889ab0956982","tid":383369,"uid":84495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解叫世界語但都係用英文?</blockquote><br />\n咁講啦，先唔理世界語呢個名<br />\n睇返Esperanto呢個名，其實係esper + anto<br />\n前者係解希望，後者就係人<br />\n佢係用Romance + Germanic + 少量Slavic嘅字為基礎，配上有邏輯有規律嘅文法而創造出嚟語言<br />\n所以講到底，就係想造一種<span style=\"color: red;\">歐洲人</span>可以好易學識嘅語言<br />\n係當年一個波蘭嘅醫生整出嚟語言<br />\n<br />\n所以唔係話用英文，只係你識英文嘅話，當然會易學<br />\n因為一嚟英文有romance同germanic來源嘅字<br />\n二嚟Esperanto都有唔少字係直頭參考英文嘅字<br />\n同埋，你識法文西班牙文都會好易上手"},{"pid":"8a81bdf23877b8cc494691174b52fc1831dd541d","tid":383369,"uid":84495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有一樣on9野就係<br />\n話明世界語，點知九成詞彙、語法都係來自歐洲語言，完全無視東亞/閃米特語言<br />\n整嗰條友真係自視過高</blockquote><br />\n我都覺，不過當年係19世紀末，佢用歐洲語言嚟整都未嘗唔合理嘅<br />\n同埋世界語呢個名純粹係中文譯名? 其實係邊個譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為整出黎果條友係想用呢個語言代替英文做世界語言嘛<br />\n文法夠簡單易學</blockquote><br />\n見過有人話如果當初Zamenhoff識中文嘅話，Esperanto可能會好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f71ff0f5492313ecdf72336ce7647df120a4b81","tid":383369,"uid":252199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nSaluton Ching!<br />\nKiel vi fartas?<br />\nMi ankaŭ nun lernas Esperanton<br />\nEsperanto estas mojosa! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}